* Photography Life评分4.6 分，满分5分， 并称其为“惊人的相机”.<ref name="PL2">{{cite web|title=Fuji X100S Review|url=http://www.photographylife.com/reviews/fuji-x100s|accessdate=25 March 2015|publisher=Photography Life|last1=Mansurov|first1=Nasim|website=www.photographylife.com|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120081211/https://photographylife.com/reviews/fuji-x100s|dead-url=no}}</ref>

